{
  "texts": [
    "These huge parameter models still need GPUs with a significant memory capacity, as the A100 (80GB), even if QLoRA lowers memory requirements during training.",
    "Finally, we note that we only experimented with the TANL framework on encoder-decoder models such as T5 and FLAN T5.",
    "Further research is necessary to verify whether our proposed method is compatible decoder-based Large Language models (LLMs) such as GPT-4 (OpenAI, 2023) and LLAMA2 (Touvron et al., 2023) 6.",
    "provides examples of these.",
    "For example, a VALUE component that reads, \"The credit reporting agencies don't automatically remove old debts,\" depends on two REASONS components."
  ]
}